ï»¿This tool presents a draft High Priority Network (HPN) that prioritizes segments and junctions with high fatal and serious injury crash rates through a combination of need and risk.


The analysis sets the groundwork for a targeted Safety Action Plan expected to be complete by Fall 2025. The analysis, utilizing 2018 â 2022 crash data through hotspot and systemic risk based analysis, underscores the critical areas where interventions can significantly enhance road safety and reduce fatal and serious injury crashes.
